name: hiODBS
description: What is HIODBS? hiODBS is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of an ODBS in the Meta-Swap pool of Fracton Protocol. HIODBS is the first NFT ETF for Otherdeed Biogenic Swamp in the world. About Otherdeed for Otherside: Otherdeed for Otherside is a collection of land plot NFTs for the Yuga Labs metaverse on the Ethereum blockchain. Each Otherdeed NFT grants holders the ability to claim Otherside land upon full Otherside launch. Each Otherdeed represents different environments and sediments within the Otherside.
